If you are starting your journey in **cloud computing**, one of the smartest and safest first steps is creating a **Cloud Free Tier account**.

Major cloud providersâ€”**Amazon Web Services (AWS)**, **Microsoft Azure**, **Google Cloud Platform (GCP)**, and **Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI)**â€”offer Free Tier accounts that allow you to **learn, experiment, and build real cloud resources** without immediate cost.

