## â˜ï¸ Stepâ€‘byâ€‘Step: Create an AWS Free Tier Account

### Step 1: Visit AWS Free Tier  
ðŸ‘‰ https://aws.amazon.com/free

### Step 2: Create an AWS Account  
Click **â€œCreate an AWS Accountâ€** and sign in using an existing Amazon account or create a new one.

### Step 3: Enter Account Information  
- Email address  
- Password  
- AWS account name  

### Step 4: Add Contact Details  
- Full name  
- Address  
- Phone number  

### Step 5: Payment Verification  
Add a credit or debit card.  
âœ… You will **not be charged** unless Free Tier limits are exceeded.

### Step 6: Phone Verification  
Enter the OTP sent to your phone.

### Step 7: Choose Support Plan  
Select **Basic Support (Free)**.

### Step 8: Sign in to AWS Console  
ðŸ‘‰ https://aws.amazon.com/console

âœ… AWS Free Tier account is ready.

