## âœ… Best Practices to Avoid Unexpected Charges

- Enable billing alerts immediately  
- Monitor usage dashboards daily  
- Stop or delete unused virtual machines  
- Remove test resources after learning  
- Never leave Free Tier workloads running unnecessarily  

